          <a
            href={links.instagram}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            className="text-pink-600 hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
          >
            üì∏ ÿßŸÜÿ≥ÿ™ÿ¨ÿ±ÿßŸÖ
